# Description
# -----------
#
#  Completion script for artisan (http://laravel.com/docs/artisan).
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Authors
# -------
#
#  * loranger (https://github.com/loranger)
#  * Yohan Tamb√® (https://github.com/Cronos87)
#
